selectComponents.lightningBoltIconText: Updates to these fields will be posted to Advantage within 24-48 hours.
selectComponents.hourglassIconText: Updates to these fields require CO approval which may delay the posting to Advantage.
selectComponents.contractorWarrantyInfoText: Contractor Warranty includes changes to the Contractor's Warranty Period, Number of Warranty Periods, Warranty Description, or Contractor Warranty is not Applicable.
selectComponents.accessoriesInfoText: Accessories includes adding or removing the mapping of an accessory to a product. (Adding or deleting a Accessory  must be done as a separate Add Product or Delete Product mod.)
selectComponents.photosInfoText: Photos changes include adding, changing, or removing photos to/from a Product.
selectComponents.deliveryInfoText: Delivery includes changes to FOB for CONUS, Alaska, Hawaii, or Puerto Rico. It also includes changes to Shipping Package Weight and Shipping Package Cube.
selectComponents.optionsInfoText: Options includes adding or deleting an option or changes to Option Group, Option Code, Option Quantity, Option Unit of Measure, Option Price, Option Description, Option Deletable? (Y/N).
selectComponents.specialChargesInfoText: Special Charges includes changes to charges for Expediting Premium, Inside Delivery, Installation, Assembly, Layout/Design, Same Day Service, One Day Service, Two Day Service, Saturday Delivery, Training.
selectComponents.specialFeaturesInfoText: Special Features includes changes to Special or Environmental Features. These items include, but are not limited to, Shipboard Use Approved, FEMP Energy Efficiency, Comprehensive Procurement Guidelines (CPG) compliant, Low VOC, US EPA Significant New Alternatives Program (SNAP) approved, BioPreferred, EPA WaterSense Program, Safer Choice, AbilityOne, UNICOR, Ergonomic, Section 508, Product 508 URL, Pre-purchased stock, Scan Code 1, Scan Code 2, Scan Code 3, Hazmat, BIFMA level, Biodegradable Products Institute compostable product, California Section 01350 standard, FloorScore, Forest Stewardship Council, Green Seal GS-01, Green Seal GS-07, Green Seal GS-37, Green Seal GS-40, Green Seal GS-41, NSF 140 Carpet, NSF 332, Pacific Northwest Snowfighters Qualified Deicers, SCAQMD Rule #1113, SCAQMD Rule #1168, STMC Toner Cartridges, UL 126, UL 2759, UL 2762, UL 2771, UL 2777, UL 2784, UL 2785, UL 2792, UL 2818 GREENGUARD. Special Features are first defined at the Offer/Contract Level, then assigned at the Line Item Level.
selectComponents.otherProductInfoText: Other Product Information includes change to Vendor Part Number, Vendor's Product/Accessory Description, UPC/ ISBN/ GTIN 14/ EAN 8/ EAN 13, Unit of Issue, Quantity Per Unit, Quantity of Product/Unit, Manufacturer Warranty, Extended Warranty, Country of Origin, Country of Origin 2, Delivery (Lead) Time Code, Delivery (Lead) Time Days, FSC/PSC, UNSPSC, NSN, Default Color, Product Length, Product Width, Product Height, Product Specific Website, Standard Pack.
